    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision 6-speed manual gearbox. The double-VANOS system is fully serviced, ensuring a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sound with a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings, the chassis retains its signature balance thanks to a tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the limited-slip differential remains tight and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A solid, performance-ready machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
