    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of reliability meeting refined style. Having been garage-kept and serviced with a 'maintenance-first' mindset, it performs beautifully in both city traffic and on long stretches of highway. Under the hood, the engine is clean and delivers power smoothly, while the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the lower valence\u2014evidence of real-world enjoyment rather than neglect. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats provide excellent support and the upholstery shows only very light softening from use. Every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly, from the dual-zone climate control to the crisp audio system. Recent preventative maintenance includes a fresh fluid service and a brake pad replacement, ensuring this car is ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality driver that has been treated with respect, this is the one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
