    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape for all your upcoming adventures! It runs super smoothly, looks great, and has been really well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 34500.0,
