    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The engine retains its signature linear power delivery via individual throttle bodies, with a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal cam timing. To address the chassis' known weak points, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, maintaining structural rigidity during high-torque loads. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein B16 dampers, offering superior rebound and compression characteristics over the stock setup. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its mileage, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including the Variable M Differential Lock and cooling system\u2014are in excellent working order. This is a visceral, analog machine optimized for the purist.",
